    "translation":{"eng":"Providence is extremely powerful and does not consider one’s religiosity or knowledge; rather, it always binds one with the ropes of karma. I do not see even the slightest means of deliverance; all I see is misery. Thus I weep, helpless and stricken with grief."}},{
